description: This 2018 Volkswagen Passat 2.0T SE, has a Reflex Silver Metallic exterior and an Moonrock Gray w/Quartz Piping interior color. 94,083 miles. Stock Number JC002668. You can connect with us by calling 407-961-7878 . No Accidents! REFLEX SILVER METALLIC This Passat has the following features: Convenience Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control; your ultimate co-pilot.Safety and Security Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe. Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it activates certain features to help prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Put your worries behind you with rear collision mitigation.Technology and Telematics Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at 407-961-7878  and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1970 SR 436 Winter Park FL 32792. We look forward to seeing you soon. description:
Discover the exceptional 2018 Nissan Sentra SV, a compact sedan that combines style, performance, and uncompromising value. With its sleek Gray exterior, this Sentra SV is more than just a practical commuter it's a testament to Nissan's commitment to engineering excellence.

Under the hood, the 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine delivers a remarkable balance of power and efficiency, with a CVT with Xtronic transmission providing a smooth and responsive driving experience. Boasting an impressive 29 city/37 highway MPG, this Sentra SV offers exceptional fuel economy, allowing you to spend less time at the pump and more time on the open road.

Beyond its impressive powertrain, the 2018 Sentra SV is brimming with a host of features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of automatic temperature control, the versatility of a split-folding rear seat, and the connectivity of the AM/FM/CD Audio System with SiriusXM radio. The Rear USB Ports (H11) and steering wheel-mounted audio controls make it easy to stay connected and in control.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Sentra SV equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear provides added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces.

Designed to exceed your expectations, the 2018 Nissan Sentra SV is a compact sedan that delivers on every level. With its impressive features, exceptional efficiency, and unwavering commitment to safety, this Sentra SV is the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Experience the difference for yourself. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this exceptional Sentra SV for a test drive. Let us demonstrate how this vehicle can enhance your driving experience and exceed your expectations. We're confident that once you experience the Sentra SV, you'll understand why it's the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

This vehicle is being sold as-is. Ingersoll Automotive will provide the vehicle inspection and reconditioning form, along with a vehicle Carfax History report. Ingersoll Automotive is not providing any implied or express coverage for repair or maintenance on this vehicle.

Elite Auto Auctions, Nationwide Online Auto Auction Platform
Dealer Name: Elite Auto Auctions
Website: EliteAutoAuctions.com
Phone: 708-722-0248

Important Notice & Inventory Location
Elite Auto Auctions operates nationwide, with vehicles stored at our main facility and at secured partner auction and storage locations across the United States.
Many vehicles are transported to our physical location for viewing or delivery.
Inspections are available by appointment only, please contact us in advance to confirm the exact vehicle location and schedule your visit.

Save Up to 70% Off Retail Prices
Why pay dealership markups? This is your opportunity to purchase quality vehicles directly through EliteAutoAuctions.com, often up to 70% below traditional retail pricing.
We provide customers with exclusive access to dealer-only and insurance auction inventory, offering exceptional nationwide selection and competitive value.

All purchases are completed online through EliteAutoAuctions.com, unless otherwise arranged in writing.

Condition & Title Transparency
Each listing clearly identifies the title status (Clean, Rebuilt, or Salvage).
Buyers are encouraged to review all photos, vehicle descriptions, and title disclosures prior to bidding or purchase.
We maintain transparency to ensure every customer understands the vehicle's history, title type, and overall condition.

Pricing & Fee Disclosure
To comply with AutoTrader pricing policies, all listings display a fixed price or a $0 Call for Price label when specific pricing is not available.

Please Note:
Sales Tax, Title, License Fee, Registration Fee, Finance Charges, Emission Testing Fees, and Compliance Fees are additional to the advertised price.
Standard fees are applied in accordance with applicable state laws and regulations.
Full pricing details and purchase terms are available on our website.

Virtual and In-Person Services
Can't visit in person? No problem!
We offer FREE virtual walk-around video presentations, showcasing every detail of any vehicle you're interested in.

We're open 7 days a week and proudly serve buyers nationwide and internationally.
To schedule an appointment, virtual showing, or for sales assistance, please call 708-722-0248 or visit EliteAutoAuctions.com.

Consistent Branding
All listings, advertisements, and customer communications are conducted exclusively under Elite Auto Auctions and EliteAutoAuctions.com.
We do not operate under alternate dealer names or URLs. This ensures consistency, transparency, and trust across all customer interactions.

Dealer Disclosure
All vehicle prices are subject to change without notice and are not guaranteed until a purchase agreement is executed.
All vehicles are sold AS-IS, unless otherwise stated in writing. Buyers are responsible for verifying all information and vehicle condition prior to purchase.

Additional Terms:

Sales Tax, Title, License, Registration, and Documentation Fees are additional and vary by state.

Financing, shipping, and extended warranty options may be available through select partners.

Mileage may vary due to test drives, transport, or storage movement.

Deposit or payment constitutes acceptance of all purchase terms and conditions listed on EliteAutoAuctions.com/terms.

Plea se review our full Terms of Use and Purchase Policy online before finalizing your transaction.
